hopobject.body: I'll put her on kiwidrug.com reviews Lending for house purchase accounted for 65 per cent of all lending in the second quarter - up from 62.4 per cent a year earlier - of which 19.1 per cent was to first-time buyers, up from 16.5 per cent a year earlier. Remortgage lending accounted for 30.4 per cent of new advances a year ago and 28.3 per cent in Q2 2013. Further advances accounted for 3 per cent of new advances in the second quarter.
